overview.en: The first standardized blockchain anti-counterfeit traceability platform in the tea industry is dedicated to the traceability and data interaction of the whole life cycle of tea planting, picking, processing, logistics and storage, and is a bridge linking the trust between tea enterprises and consumers.
overview.zh: 茶行业首个标准化区块链防伪溯源平台，致力于茶叶种植、采摘、加工、物流、仓储全生命周期的溯源和数据交互，是链接茶企和消费者之间信任的桥梁。
